Analysis.name: Incidence of hypotension requiring vascular expansion
Bias.arising.from.the.randomization.proc: Randomization was performed through a centralised telephone assignment stratified by center. According to the previously published Cochrane review, concealment was achieved through a central and pharmacy controlled allocation.
